name: PSYC 170
title: Psychopathology
description: Survey of theory, research, and intervention in human psychopathology. Covers psychological, biological, developmental, and socio-cultural approaches. (Formerly offered as Abnormal Psychology.)

pre_req_data.text: Prerequisite(s): PSYC 100; PSYC 60 highly recommended as preparation.

class_notes: Enroll in lecture and associated discussion section
